{"name":"Raaste","shortname":"raaste","subtext":"Summer 2024","year":2024,"content":["behte hai yeh raaste,","kehte hai mujhe:","kho le khudko ae musafir,","ro le zara,","baahon mein meri.","dekhi hai maine bhi,","door se aahatein teri.","","kitna sahega ae musafir?","kab tak rahega chup?","roosa hai jahaan tujhse,","gussa hai sab.","kaanch hi toh toota hai,","jud jayega,","haale dil ki tarah.","","soona sa lag raha hai na,","aaj yeh jug saara?","baadalon mein chupa hua sa tu,","mere chaand ka ek toota taara.","koi nahi dekhega, bahaar aaja,","taraste hai hum tere liye,","bas apne geet ke do shab'd tu gaa-ja.","","behte hai yeh raaste,","kehte hai mujhe:","kho le khudko ae musafir,","rehne mein yahan ab,","rakha bhi kya hai aakhir?"]}
